title: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Sweden Roads, Northern Sweden, 2008
name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Sweden Roads, Northern Sweden, 2008
description: This Dataset is part of three downloaded from the openstreetmap, Geofabrik website and includes information and locations of roads throughout northern Sweden. The dataset includes Road names and type. Type of road includes information on whether the road is a primary, residential or secondary road, etc. Because the dataset for the entire country was too big, it was divided into northern, southeastern and southwestern Sweden.
